p>已宣布将于 6 月 13 日至 16 日演出的其他演员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maggie-rogers">Maggie Rogers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dominic-fike">Dominic Fike</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzy-mcalpine">Lizzy McAlpine</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/interpol">Interpol</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/parcels">Parcels</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brittany-howard">Brittany Howard</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jason-isbell">Jason Isbell and the 400 Unit</a> 、Fisher 和更多的。</p><p>去年，Hebden<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">再次</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a>和 Fred 联手，结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coachella">Coachella 音乐节</a>的第二个周末。周日，他们在主舞台上接替了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>之后的“TBA”时段，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-ocean-blink-182-coachella-weekend-2-3432864">Frank Ocean 在音乐节前夕因腿部骨折，按照医生的指示退出了 Coachella Weekend 2</a> 。</p><p>此前，三人曾在纽约麦迪逊广场花园同台演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skrillex-fred-again-four-tet-announce-surprise-show-new-york-3399251">惊喜演出几分钟之内就被抢购一空</a>。</p><p> <i>《NME》</i>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/skrillex-live-in-new-york-city-a-once-in-a-lifetime-rave-at-the-garden-3401021">该剧的四星评论</a>中表示：“当舞曲从花园的墙壁上弹起时，不仅由于霓虹灯的快速闪烁，场地呈现出不同的色调，而且能量也不同了。过道里的粉丝挤满了人，但尽管场地拥挤，每个人都同步跳舞，这证明了成千上万的狂欢者之间的联系不仅仅是他们快速购买门票的能力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tets-all-dayer-festival-returns-to-london-this-summer-3591331">今年夏天，春节四日全天音乐节将重返伦敦，</a>并首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ;
 《沙丘：第二部分》因其“史诗般”的规模和雄心壮志而受到好评https://www.nme.com/news/film/dune-part-two-praished-for-its-epic-scale-and-ambition-in-glowing-first-reviews-3591254?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=沙丘第二部分因其史诗般的规模和首次评论中的野心而受到赞誉Chris EdwardsThu, 22 Feb 2024 11:07:35 +0000 Film NewsNewsdenisDune https://www.nme.com/?p=3591254 <p><img width="2000" height="1260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-400x252.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-800x504.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-696x438.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1392x877.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1068x673.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “它不同于现有的任何其他大片”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dune-part-two-praised-for-its-epic-scale-and-ambition-in-glowing-first-reviews-3591254">《沙丘：第二部分》的帖子因其“史诗般”的规模和在首次评论中的雄心壮志而受到称赞，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-400x252.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-800x504.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-696x438.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1392x877.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1068x673.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune-part-2"><em>《沙丘：第二部分》的</em></a>第一批评论即将发布，评论家们对丹尼斯·维伦纽瓦的“史诗”科幻续集赞不绝口。</p><p><em>第二部分</em>根据弗兰克·赫伯特 1965 年的 896 页小说改编，讲述保罗·阿特雷迪斯（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西</a>·查拉梅饰）与查尼（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">赞达亚饰</a>）和弗里曼人联合起来，学习沙漠之道，向摧毁他家庭的势力发动战争的故事，并作为所谓的被选中者履行他的命运。</p><p>目前，该片在<a href="https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dune_part_two" target="_blank" rel="noopener">烂番茄</a>上的 115 条评论中得分高达 97%，只有 3 条负面评论。</p><p>许多人称赞续集的宏大范围和野心，其中包括<em><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/tv-movies/tv-movie-reviews/dune-part-two-review-1234962710/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《滚石》杂志</a></em>的大卫·菲尔 (David Fear)，他写道：“维伦纽夫已经超越了自己。更重要的是，他公正地对待了一块被石头点燃的试金石后半部的范围、规模和纯粹的怪异，而没有用双关语打磨掉它的边缘。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2024/feb/21/dune-part-two-review-denis-villeneuve" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>的彼得·布拉德肖 (Peter Bradshaw) 表示， <em>《沙丘：</em><em>第二部分》</em> “出色地向我们展示了一个完整的创造世界，一个独特且毫无疑问的宇宙，这可能会被大量模仿：电影摄影师格雷格·弗雷泽和美术指导帕特里斯·维梅特的胜利。汉斯·季默的配乐提供了恰到好处的基调，既沉稳又宏伟。” </p><figure id="attachment_3590128" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3590128" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3590128" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Florence-Pugh-in-Dune_-Part-Two-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3590128" class="wp-caption-text">弗洛伦斯·皮尤在《沙丘：第二部分》中。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时， <a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/reviews/dune-2-review-timothee-chalamet-denis-villeneuve-1235917934/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》</em></a>承认将电影分成两半是一场“豪赌”，但不知何故得到了回报。 “无论你做什么，都不要把这部续集误认为是续集。这是一个传奇的后半部分，”他们写道。</p><p><a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/dune-part-two/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》</em></a>还对这部电影给予了热烈的评价，写道：“有很多板块在旋转——而且在大多数情况下，维伦纽夫对它们都表现出了非凡的控制力。除此之外，他还编排了令人惊叹的序列，让你惊呆在座位后面，”他补充道，其中的许多序列都是“声音和视觉上的压倒性壮举，雷鸣般的低音将把任何普通电影院变成令人颤抖的 4DX 体验”。</p><p>为数不多的负面评论之一来自<a href="https://www.indiewire.com/criticism/movies/dune-part-two-movie-review-1234955419/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>IndieWire</em></a>的大卫·埃利希 (David Ehrlich)，他表示这部电影“令人震惊，但又令人痛苦”。</p><p>埃利希写道：“这部新电影不仅准确地接续了上一章的内容，而且还继承了前一章令人惊讶但又乏味的优点和缺点。” </p><figure id="attachment_3590123" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3590123" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3590123" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Austin-Butler-and-Lea-Seydoux-in-Dune_-Part-Two-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3590123" class="wp-caption-text">奥斯汀·巴特勒和蕾雅·赛杜在《沙丘：第二部分》中。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>另一条负面评论来自<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-reviews/dune-part-two-review-timothee-chalamet-zendaya-1235830061/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>的 Lovia Gyarkye，她称赞这部时长 2 小时 46 分钟的电影是比第一部电影更大的“电影事件”，但批评其肤浅。</p><p> “第二部分在描绘弗雷曼人（一个在帝国内争取自决权的土著人民）时，受到了一种令人烦恼的肤浅的困扰；这部电影很难完全体现赫伯特的反帝国和生态反乌托邦文本的细微差别，”Gyarkye 写道。</p><p>尽管如此，影评人的共识仍然是压倒性的积极， <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/dune-2-review-ratings-zendaya-timothee-chalamet-b2500367.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《独立报》</em></a>将其描述为“完全的感官和想象力的沉浸”，并补充说它“不同于现有的任何其他大片”。</p><p><strong><em>沙丘：第二部</em>将于 3 月 1 日上映。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dune-part-two-praised-for-its-epic-scale-and-ambition-in-glowing-first-reviews-3591254">《沙丘：第二部分》的帖子因其“史诗般”的规模和在首次评论中的雄心壮志而受到称赞，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
